Marquis of Queensberry.

1035
01:00:51,691 --> 01:00:54,520
John Sholto Douglas,
Marquis of Queensberry.

1036
01:00:56,740 --> 01:00:58,611
[PEOPLE MURMURING]

1037
01:01:05,270 --> 01:01:06,793
[MURMURING STOPS]

1038
01:01:08,839 --> 01:01:11,885
Are you
John Sholto Douglas,
Marquis of Queensberry?

1039
01:01:12,669 --> 01:01:14,366
