dreadful accusations.

1432
01:20:41,488 --> 01:20:45,318
I know, Sir Edward. It was
unforgivably stupid of me,

1433
01:20:45,362 --> 01:20:48,408
but I was afraid you
wouldn'’t take the case.

1434
01:20:50,149 --> 01:20:52,325
